data.description: What more could you want! Beautiful updates throughout this entire 1,630 square foot home! 4 generous bedrooms and 2 bathrooms situated on a large corner lot. The primary has double closets, dual sinks, and tile shower. Guest bathroom offers dual sinks and beautiful tile shower tub combo. Kitchen boasts granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances, and polished cement flooring. The kitchen opens up to the great room that features built in shelves and mantel that surround the fireplace insert. Backyard offers plenty of space for entertainging along with an inground pool & slide! Top it all off with solar, four car garage, additional fenced storage, and room for RV parking!
